The first production 'D's out the factory door came without the dorsal
fin.  It was added to the line later.  IIRC, the original Airfix Mustang
came without the fin and the Heller kit came with the option of using or
not using the fin.  I took the parts and added them to a 'B' I was
building.  Thus I had a D without the dorsal and a B with.

