horizontal stabilizer will not withstand the effects of a snap roll. To
prevent recurrence the stabilizer should be reinforced in accordance
with T.O. 01-60J-18 dated 8 April &lt;/wiki/April_8&gt; 1944 &lt;/wiki/1944&gt; and
a dorsal fin should be installed. Dorsal fin kits are being made
available to overseas activities"

While some existing aircraft do not have the dorsal extension fitted,
